            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>美國知名媒體娛樂公司華納兄弟探索集團（Warner Bros. Discovery）宣佈其全球串流平台 Max 將於 2024 年 11 月 19 日正式登陸香港及東南亞市場。此次擴展象徵著 Max 繼美國、拉丁美洲及歐洲成功推出後，進一步進軍香港、台灣、新加坡、馬來西亞、印尼、菲律賓及泰國等 7 個新市場。Max 匯聚了多個深受全球觀眾喜愛的品牌內容，包括華納兄弟、HBO、DC 宇宙、卡通頻道等，為用戶提供多元化的娛樂體驗。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269310" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/maxinsoutheastasiata-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/maxinsoutheastasiata-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/maxinsoutheastasiata.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>訂閲 Max 即可觀賞  HBO、哈利波特、DC 宇宙、卡通頻道、Max 原創系列等廣受歡迎的品牌；亦有多部荷李活熱門電影、Discovery 頻道、TLC 、AFN、Food Network、探索調查頻道 Investigation Discovery 和 HGTV 的精彩節目。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269312" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_aquamanandthelos-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_aquamanandthelos-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_aquamanandthelos-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269313" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_aquamanandthelos-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_aquamanandthelos-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_aquamanandthelos-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom</p><p>Max 以其豐富的劇集、電影及紀錄片著稱，當中包括多部熱門作品如《哈利波特（Harry Potter）》系列、《老友記（Friends）》、熱門同名遊戲改編劇集《最後生還者（The Last of Us）》、《龍族前傳（House of the Dragon）》以及《沙丘瀚戰：第二章（Dune: Part Two）》。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269328" style="text-align: center;" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_friends-694x540.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="540" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_friends-694x540.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_friends-1156x900.jpg 1156w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_friends-scaled.jpg 1157w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《老友記（Friends）》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269314" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_duneparttwo_002-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_duneparttwo_002-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_duneparttwo_002-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《沙丘瀚戰：第二章（Dune: Part Two）》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269315" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_duneparttwo_001-694x366.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="366" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_duneparttwo_001-694x366.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_duneparttwo_001-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《沙丘瀚戰：第二章（Dune: Part Two）》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269323" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_thelastofusseaso-464x580.jpg" alt="" width="464" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_thelastofusseaso-464x580.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_thelastofusseaso.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 464px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《最後生還者（The Last of Us）》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269324" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_thelastofusseaso-1-464x580.jpg" alt="" width="464" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_thelastofusseaso-1-464x580.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_thelastofusseaso-1.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 464px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《最後生還者（The Last of Us）》</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269325" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_thelastofusseaso-2-464x580.jpg" alt="" width="464" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_thelastofusseaso-2-464x580.jpg 464w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_thelastofusseaso-2.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 464px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《最後生還者（The Last of Us）》</p><p>此外，Max 原創內容亦備受期待，如《沙丘：預言（Dune: Prophecy）》及 James Gunn 和 Peter Safran 上任 DC 宇宙後最新推出的成人動畫《Creature Commandos》。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269319" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_duneprophecy_tea-391x580.jpg" alt="" width="391" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_duneprophecy_tea-391x580.jpg 391w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_duneprophecy_tea.jpg 607w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 391px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《沙丘：預言（Dune: Prophecy）》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269322" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_duneprophecy_jih-694x347.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_duneprophecy_jih-694x347.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/hbo_duneprophecy_jih.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《沙丘：預言（Dune: Prophecy）》</p><p>用戶訂閲 Max 後亦可觀賞兒童品牌 Cartoon Network 和 CARTOONITO，<br />容，由《探險活寶（Adventure Time）》、《熊熊遇見你（We Bare Bears）》、《Tom and Jerry》、《樂一通（Looney Tunes） 》到《少年悍將 GO！（Teen Titans Go!）》等應有盡有。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269330" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_adventuretime_00-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_adventuretime_00-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_adventuretime_00.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《探險活寶（Adventure Time）》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1269331" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_adventuretime_00-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_adventuretime_00-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_adventuretime_00-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《探險活寶（Adventure Time）》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269332" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_looneytunes_002-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_looneytunes_002-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_looneytunes_002.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《樂一通（Looney Tunes） 》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269333" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_looneytunes_001-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_looneytunes_001-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_looneytunes_001.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《樂一通（Looney Tunes） 》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269334" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_tomandjerry_001-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_tomandjerry_001-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_tomandjerry_001-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《Tom and Jerry》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269335" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_tomandjerry_002-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_tomandjerry_002-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_tomandjerry_002-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《Tom and Jerry》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1269336" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_webarebears_001-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_webarebears_001-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_webarebears_001-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《熊熊遇見你（We Bare Bears）》</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1269337" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_webarebears_002-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_webarebears_002-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/max_webarebears_002-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲《熊熊遇見你（We Bare Bears）》</p><p>從 11 月 19 日起，訂戶可透過 Max.com 官方網站及指定合作夥伴選擇不同的訂閲方案，並享有包括多個獨立帳戶及個人化推薦功能的升級觀影體驗。此外，兒童用戶亦可享有專屬帳戶及家長監控功能，提升家庭使用便利性。隨著 Max 的登陸，香港用戶將能夠在各種裝置上輕鬆享受這個全新串流平台帶來的視聽盛宴。現有 HBO GO 訂戶將會於 11 月 19 日自動成為 Max 訂戶，Max 將於未來數星期將陸續公佈更多詳情。</p><h2>訂閲方案：</h2><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;"><tbody><tr><td style="width: 23.9429%;"> </td><td style="width: 38.9621%; height: 24px;">標準方案</td><td style="width: 70.4283%; height: 24px;">高級方案</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 23.9429%;">同時觀看裝置數：</td><td style="width: 38.9621%; height: 24px;">同時使用 2 部裝置觀看</td><td style="width: 70.4283%; height: 24px;">同時使用 4 部裝置觀看</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 23.9429%;">影片解像度：</td><td style="width: 38.9621%; height: 24px;">全高清影片解像度</td><td style="width: 70.4283%; height: 24px;">4K UHD 和 Dolby Atmos（按影片而定）</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 23.9429%;">跨裝置觀看功能：</td><td style="width: 38.9621%; height: 24px;">跨裝置觀看功能，包括電視</td><td style="width: 70.4283%; height: 24px;">跨裝置觀看功能，包括電視</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 23.9429%;">可下載影片數量：</td><td style="width: 38.9621%; height: 24px;">下載多達 30 套影片以便隨時隨地觀賞</td><td style="width: 70.4283%; height: 24px;">下載多達 100 套影片以便隨時隨地觀賞（設有上限）</td></tr></tbody></table><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/18/iphone16proreview/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iPhone 16 Pro Max 詳細開箱影片，並非只「多了顆掣」</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/10/iphone-16-%e7%b3%bb%e5%88%97-pro-max-%e5%a4%96%e5%aa%92%e4%b8%8a%e6%89%8b%e8%a9%95%e6%b8%ac-%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba%e6%9c%80%e6%84%9b-18-%e5%80%8b%e5%8a%9f%e8%83%bd-apple-watch-s10-%e5%8f%8a-airpods-4/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iPhone 16 系列 Pro Max 外媒上手評測，港人最愛 18 個功能</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/07/gurman-apple-to-launch-new-m4-macs-and-ipad-mini-7-on-november-1/software/mac-os-x/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">M4 Mac、iPad mini 7 或於 11 月發佈　同時推出 M4 Pro、Max 版 Mac 電腦</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/15/warner-bro-max-streaming-coming-to-hong-kong-19-november/movie-2/">華納兄弟 Max 串流服務登陸香港　下月 19 日起有得睇</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
