        </item>
        <item>
            <title>實惠「多謝支持」帖文被誤解結業 　網民：結業潮「呃 Like」黑心 + IKEA 即出抽水文</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/15/pricerite/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=pricerite</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/15/pricerite/life-tech/social-network/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 08:00:13 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[社交網絡]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Facebook]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[IKEA]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[實惠]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1269178</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今日（15 日）凌晨 0 時香港傢俬品牌實惠在 Facebook 張貼了一則 8 字帖文：「多謝各位　多年支持」引起網民熱議。事緣因其日前剛剛推出週年優惠售出大量傢具，有訂購了傢俬的網民要求實惠「頂到月尾」，因為其預訂的梳化尚未到貨。最後實惠在今晨 9 點再發帖文，表示僅是開展新一輪減價。有網民認為實惠在結業潮下為「呃 like」發出這種帖文非常黑心。</p><p>實惠在今日凌晨 0 時發布以下帖文，下面有網民揣測其是否要「畢業」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269183" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_1-472x580.jpg" alt="" width="472" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_1-472x580.jpg 472w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_1.jpg 697w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 472px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/GQq6L92gWi9ZCNvN/">實惠 Facebook</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269203" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015150451-1-694x179.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="179" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015150451-1-694x179.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015150451-1.jpg 1092w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有網民詢問實惠是否「完成歷史任務，可以『畢業』了」<br />
圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/GQq6L92gWi9ZCNvN/">實惠 Facebook</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269216" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015152956-694x115.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="115" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015152956-694x115.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015152956.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲訂購了梳化的網友顯得徬徨，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/GQq6L92gWi9ZCNvN/">實惠 Facebook</a></p><p>香港知名網上討論區 LIHKG 有網民發帖指，實惠在結業潮下利用這種形式「呃 Like」非常黑心，又斥實惠不應該在這個時勢下開這種玩笑。下面有網民則回應表示擔心實惠會結業，不知道應否繼續訂貨。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269202" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_5-694x267.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="267" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_5-694x267.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_5.jpg 1123w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3803349/page/1">LIHKG</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269204" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_6-694x154.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="154" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_6-694x154.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_6.jpg 881w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://lih.kg/mioOtT">LIHKG</a></p><p>最終實惠在今日（15 日）早上 9 時正再發新帖文，表示僅是為新優惠價錢造勢宣傳，下面引來網民劣評如潮。有網民在下面回應指，已經沒有信心再預訂任何產品，擔心此為「執笠」先兆。另外有網民客觀分析，指實惠這次市場推廣行動不濟，更稱自己已經訂購了價值數千元貨物，看見實惠的 8 字帖文會覺得緊張是人之常情。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269205" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015151400-396x580.jpg" alt="" width="396" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015151400-396x580.jpg 396w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015151400.jpg 615w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 396px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/gJ2rjqjWy8WzmhwU/">實惠 Facebook</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269206" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_8-694x115.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="115" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_8-694x115.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_8.jpg 781w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/gJ2rjqjWy8WzmhwU/">實惠 Facebook</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269207" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_9-694x267.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="267" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_9-694x267.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/pricerite_9.jpg 780w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/gJ2rjqjWy8WzmhwU/">實惠 Facebook</a></p><p>事件亦引來 IKEA Facebook 專頁小編出來抽水，發文表示今日是「國際小編感謝日」，帖文與實惠相似，但最後加上了「小編」兩隻細字，表示感激各方支持 IKEA Facebook 頁面管理員。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1269209" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015152040-409x580.jpg" alt="" width="409" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015152040-409x580.jpg 409w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/20241015152040.jpg 635w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 409px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/NJSrPY3tMKra5ZtN/">IKEA Facebook</a></p><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://www.pricerite.com.hk/hk/zh/storeInfo/">實惠官網</a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/GQq6L92gWi9ZCNvN/">實惠 Facebook</a>、<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3803349/page/1">LIHKG</a>、<a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/p/NJSrPY3tMKra5ZtN/">IKEA Facebook</a><br /><b>相關文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/01/facebook-icon/life-tech/social-network/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Facebook 應用程式圖示亂變色，原來是技術性錯誤</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/15/pricerite/life-tech/social-network/">實惠「多謝支持」帖文被誤解結業 　網民：結業潮「呃 Like」黑心 + IKEA 即出抽水文</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
